OL,3,CUkraine has 'clear right' to use
OL,4,CBritish weapons on Russian soil, MoD
OL,5,Csays
OL,7,FUkrainian forces are free to use
OL,8,Fweapons given to them by the UK during
OL,9,Ftheir ongoing incursion onto Russian
OL,10,Fsoil, the Ministry of Defence (MoD)
OL,11,Fhas suggested.
OL,13,FIt comes as Ukraine claims to have
OL,14,Fmade more territorial gains and
OL,15,Fcaptured more than 100 Russian
OL,16,Fprisoners of war during its ongoing
OL,17,Fadvancement into Russia's Kursk region.
