OL,3,CUkraine has 'clear right' to use
OL,4,CBritish weapons on Russian soil, MoD
OL,5,Csays
OL,7,FSince the incursion began, over
OL,8,F132,000 people have been evacuated and
OL,9,F74 villages in the region are now
OL,10,Funder Ukrainian control.
OL,12,FThe MoD has said said Ukraine has a
OL,13,F"clear right" to use weapons donated
OL,14,Fby the UK for its self-defence, and
OL,15,Fstated there had been no change in
OL,16,Fpolicy since Labour came to power.
