OL,3,CUkraine has 'clear right' to use
OL,4,CBritish weapons on Russian soil, MoD
OL,5,Csays
OL,7,F"There has been no change in UK
OL,8,FGovernment policy, under Article 51 of
OL,9,Fthe UN Charter Ukraine has a clear
OL,10,Fright of self-defence against Russia's
OL,11,Fillegal attacks, that does not
OL,12,Fpreclude operations inside Russia," an
OL,13,FMoD spokesman said.
OL,15,F"We make clear during the gifting
OL,16,Fprocess that equipment is to be used
OL,17,Fin line with international law."
