OL,7,FDowning Street has previously insisted
OL,8,Fthey are only to be used for conflict
OL,9,Fwithin Ukraine. They were first gifted
OL,10,Fby the British government in 2022.
OL,12,FIn April 2024, then-Prime Minister
OL,13,FRishi Sunak announced a #500 million
OL,14,Faid package for Ukraine, with supplies
OL,15,Fincluding 400 vehicles, 1,600
OL,16,Fmunitions and 4 million rounds of
OL,17,Fammunition.
